page.title: 13My Hobbies in Seaton Burn
page.content: I like playing{snooker}at the Seaton Burn Youth Club and I like{B.M.X. riding. We go to{Brownies}at half past five. We play 'There's a Little Sand Girl' 'Bunny Hops'. We do badges. Our sixes are called the Ghillie Dhus,Imps Sprites and the Kelpies. I have got four badges.I have got Hostess, Artist Safety in the Home, House Orderly.I am doing First Aid and Musician. We pay 20p for subs. You leave Brownies when you are ten. It ends at 7.00.We go to the park in the Summer. At the park we play{Leapfrog}and we play on other things as well. We have a proper uniform. I go to the B.M.X. bike course at the Welfare. My hobby is playing{snooker}or darts in my house. Every weekend I go to the{Play {Scheme}another hobby is playing with my{Video Games.
